  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2023-03-29",
    "date": "2023-11-14T20:48:05Z",
    "text": "Justice for Exploited Children Act of 2023\n\nThis bill replaces the current maximum civil penalty of $11,000 for a violation of the child labor laws with a minimum civil penalty of $5,000 and a maximum of $132,270 (or, in the case of a violation that causes death or serious injury, $25,000 and $601,150, respectively)."
  },
